Renegade - Bomb-Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists from bombing biological weapon crates. Team members must defuse any bombs that threaten targeted areas.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the C4 must destroy one of the biological weapon stashes. Other Notes: There are 2 biological weapon stashes in the mission.

32 spawn points
